{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I am backtracking, but we are talking about-- there has been so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so much was going on around that time that things do get a bit compressed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was-- he came back from the Russian front in December 1943 with terrible stories about-- how should I put it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did he put it?-- about bad houses where Jewish girls are taken to service the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was talking about brothels set up by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this is 1943, and we still didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was very upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told my father and mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the question came, what do we do with the young girls, which included me and two of my cousins?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember there was a very serious family discussion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And again, my father said, how can one believe such horrible things?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After all, enemies are enemies but human beings are human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we cannot let our child-- because the idea was to send me and my two cousins away with-- with-- we had a washer woman, a  peasant, a Romanian peasant washer woman, who came once a week to do the heavy washing-- there were no washing machines-- and that she would keep us there, God forbid, if something should happen.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But again, people are people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cannot do these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And besides, the Russians are rolling from east to west.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the final thing was, we cannot let our child go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so did my uncle, the father of my two cousins, say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My other brother, Alex, he was also in this Jewish labor brigade, but he somehow managed to stay in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His second child was born two days before Eichmann came to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
